tion":"Rewrote all 4 implementation-biased hook prompts (Stop, TaskCompleted, SubagentStop, TeammateIdle) in .claude/settings.json to be context-aware: the new text explicitly branches on task type (code changes vs read-only vs infrastructure/docs) and instructs the hook reader to NOT produce generic 'cannot verify' responses when criteria don't apply. Fix is live immediately — no session restart needed because Claude Code re-reads settings.json prompts on each hook fire. Verified JSON validity post-edit."},"task_lines":[],"tasks":{},"codeblock_ranges":[]},